{"books":[{"id":"jfjb","name":"解放军报","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"","files":[],"article":{"dates":[{"year":1966,"month":8,"day":13}],"page_start":2,"page_end":2,"description":"","is_range_date":false,"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"title":"毛主席万岁！万万岁！","authors":["刘一步"],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"“毛主席万岁！万万岁！”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一阵阵欢呼声，一阵阵春"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"雷，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"滚过了万里晴空，飞越了千山万水。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毛主席站在我们身边，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一轮红日，万丈光辉，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"照得革命人民心头暖，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"映得祖国山河分外美。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"多少颗火热的心在跳动，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"多少双眼里滚出喜悦的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"泪，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"领袖的心和我们的心贴在"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一起，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"千言万语凝成一句心里"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"话：“毛主席万岁！”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"握一握毛主席的手，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"身上干劲增千倍；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"听一听毛主席的话，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"文化革命起风雷。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“你们要关心国家大事，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"要把无产阶级文化大革命"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"进行到底！”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"字字如同进军的战鼓，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"革命群众的队伍健步如"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"飞。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"按照您的指示，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们誓把旧世界砸得粉"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"碎！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"按照您的指示，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们要建造出一个共产主"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"义新社会！"}],"alias":""},"tags":[{"type":"文稿类型","name":"文章"}]}]}